Package no.hiof.webframework.application.frontend

Class HtmlPageBuilder

java.lang.Object
no.hiof.webframework.application.frontend.HtmlPageBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
IHtmlBuilder
public class HtmlPageBuilder extends Object implements IHtmlBuilder
This class implements the IHtmlBuilder interface and can be used to build a custom HTML page.
